Trim the @pak choi{1}, then separate the leaves. Cut any larger leaves in half
lengthways down the middle.

Peel and grate the @garlic clove{2}(peeled and grated) (or use a #garlic press{}).

In a #small bowl{}, combine the @ketjap manis{25%g}, @tomato ketchup{2%tbsp},
@water for the sauce{2%tbsp}, @sriracha sauce{15%g}, @rice vinegar{11%ml} and
@soy sauce{12.5%ml}. Season with @ground black pepper{}, then set your sticky
sauce aside.

== Spicy Smacked Cucumber ==

Trim the @cucumber{1}, then pop onto a #board{} and use a #rolling pin{} to
gently smack it a few times until split. Cut into roughly 2cm chunks.

In a #medium bowl{}, combine the cucumber, @sugar{1%tsp}, remaining
@rice vinegar{11%ml}, @soy sauce{12.5%ml} and @sriracha sauce{15%g}. Season with
@salt{} and @ground black pepper{}, then set aside.

== Sweet Chilli Gyozas ==

Heat a drizzle of @oil{} in a #large frying pan{} on medium-high heat.

Once hot, add the @vegetable gyozas{1%pack} and fry until golden on the bottom,
~{2-3%minutes}. Reduce the heat to medium-low, add @water{1%tbsp} and immediately
cover with a #lid{} or some #foil{}. Cook until piping hot, ~{3-4%minutes}.

Add the @sweet chilli sauce{64%g} to the pan and turn to coat the gyozas,
~{1%minute}. Transfer to a medium bowl and cover to keep warm.

== Sticky Veggie Udon Noodles ==

Wipe out the (now empty) #frying pan{} and return to high heat with a drizzle
of @oil{}.

Once hot, add the @sliced mushrooms{120%g} to the pan. Season with @salt{} and
@ground black pepper{} and fry, stirring occasionally, until browned,
~{5-6%minutes}.

Add the pak choi and garlic. Fry until fragrant, ~{1%minute}.

Once the veg is tender, pour in the sticky sauce. Bring to the boil and simmer
until reduced, ~{2-3%minutes}.

Add the @udon noodles{220%g} to the pan. Toss to coat and simmer until piping
hot, ~{1-2%minutes}.

== To Serve ==

Share the sticky veggie udon between your #bowls{} and top with the sweet chilli
gyozas.

Sprinkle over the @crispy onions{1%sachet} to finish.

Serve the smacked cucumber alongside.

Enjoy!